graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.27+ /<br/>OpenShift 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine v2| ArgoWF[Argo Workflows 3.5.14]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine v1| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage]
    DSPO -->|metadata persistence| MySQL[MySQL/MariaDB 10.3+]
    DSPO -->|authentication| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy v4.12+]

    %% Optional External Dependencies
    DSPO -.->|service mesh<br/>optional| Envoy[Envoy Proxy<br/>OSSM 2.x]
    DSPO -.->|certificate mgmt<br/>optional| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSPO -->|external access| Route[OpenShift Route]
    DSPO -.->|mTLS<br/>optional| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio]

    %% Integration Points (Outbound)
    DSPO -->|model serving| KServe[KServe]
    DSPO -->|distributed compute| Ray[Ray]
    DSPO -->|API server access| K8sAPIServer[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Integration Points (Inbound)
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models| KServe
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| DSPO
    Users[Data Scientists] -->|create pipelines| DSPO

    %% External Services (Optional)
    DSPO -.->|external DB<br/>production| ExternalDB[External MySQL/MariaDB]
    DSPO -.->|external storage<br/>production| ExternalS3[AWS S3 / Compatible]
    DSPO -.->|container images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry]

    %% Operator Dependencies
    DSPO -->|controller runtime| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime]
    DSPO -->|structured logging| Zap[Zap Logger]
    DSPO -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus Operator]

    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px

    %% External Required Dependencies
    style K8s fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
